{"word":"G2119 - εὐκαιρέω - eukairéō - yoo-kahee-reh'-o - Have leisure","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὐκαιρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eukairéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">yoo-kahee-reh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Have leisure</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பொழுதுபோக்கு, சமயம், நற்சமயம்"},{"paragraph":"to have good time, opportunity, leisure"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2121 - εὔκαιρος - eúkairos - yoo'-kahee-ros/2121\">G2121</a>; to <i>have good time</i>, that is, <i>opportunity</i> or <i>leisure:</i> - have leisure (convenient time), spend time.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}